---
import SectionLabel from "./SectionLabel.astro";
---

<section class="reveal" id="about">
  <SectionLabel index="01" label="about" />
  <div class="side text-[0.95rem] leading-relaxed text-subtext1 space-y-3.5">
    <p>
      Hey! I'm <span class="text-peach font-semibold">Hunter</span> — an indie
      developer who likes shipping browser games, real-time multiplayer apps,
      Rust TUIs, and native macOS utilities.
    </p>
    <p>
      If it can run in a browser, a terminal, or a menu bar, I've probably
      built one. Currently obsessing over real-time multiplayer, beautiful
      system tools, and procedurally generated music for tiny browser games.
    </p>
    <p class="text-overlay1">
      This site is built with
      <a href="https://astro.build" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-blue underline decoration-blue/30 underline-offset-2">Astro</a>
      &nbsp;+&nbsp;
      <a href="https://svelte.dev" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-red underline decoration-red/30 underline-offset-2">Svelte</a>,
      themed with <span class="text-mauve">Catppuccin Frappé</span>, and
      hosted on GitHub Pages. Source is
      <a href="https://github.com/8tp/chuds.dev" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-peach underline decoration-peach/30 underline-offset-2">on GitHub</a>.
    </p>
    <p class="font-mono text-xs text-overlay0 pt-1">
      <span class="text-green">$</span> philosophy: if it's worth building, it's worth over-engineering at 2 AM
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
